data.description: All brick rancher on 0.35 acre lot. Horseshoe shaped driveway for easy ingress/egress. Seller has made these expensive improvements: all new backyard privacy fence, new electric panel box in 2020  (includes generator connection), all new HVAC (2023), new electric water heater (2023), and 8x10 aluminum shed. Spacious living room with stone fireplace with tile hearth. Enclosed porch with tile floor off living room. Two full baths and each has a bathtub/shower combination. Hardwood floors in living room and bedrooms. Attic could be fully finished to add to living square footage.
